The new spell parameters should put shaman heals on the same ratio that they were for Planes of Power spells:<br />
<br />
Supernal Light: 2750<br />
Nature’s Infusion: 1750<br />
Tnarg’s Mending: 1300<br />
<br />
Comparatively for HP/Second:<br />
Supernal Light:  100%<br />
Nature’s Infusion: 64%<br />
Tnarg’s Mending: 47%<br />
<br />
