<br />
Again, sorry I didn’t get this info out earlier, and for letting the bad mana cost on Breath of Trushar go live.  There’s really no excuse for that blunder.<br />
<br />
-Ryan</i><hr size="1" /></blockquote>While I can appriciate keeping things comparatively the same I do feel at this point that the relative numbers may need some adjusting for shaman in god. The high dps, low hps mobs making quick fights and the increased fequency of slow mitigating mobs and amount they mitigate slow for have left shaman in a relatively weaker position than previous expansions. Improving our heals will help us compensate and contribute more in GoD situations.</p>
	
	
	
