	<p>I'll post this again, since no one will probably read how I edited my post. Feel free to disagree, but I doubt you can, really.<br />
<br />
Edit: Started this post before Rytan posted, so I am going to add something.<br />
You're right, Rytan. Our heals will now be just as balanced as they were pre-GoD and in part this board is resonsible for making it sound as if the problems with healing only exist since GoD, when in reality they were already present in PoP and LDoN. <br />
