	<td class="alt2" valign="top">
	
	<!-- message -->
	<p>Lit, <br />
<br />
Question though.  From what I'm reading, to even hack it in GoD you really need to be almost time geared (or close to it).  Otherwise you're going to run into some problems.  Not that it *can't* be done, but it definitely seems that in order to really get into the heart of GoD you need to be darn well equipped/AA'd. <br />
<br />
In short, shouldn't (or at least couldn't) it be assumed that you will have the AAs maxed in the areas that these upgrades are aimed at?<br />
<br />
I don't hunt in GoD - shoot my main is still only 62 and I'm by no means ever going to raid anything bigger than the PoJ trials heh (yes I know it's not a raid) - but I can see where the idea that you should be almost max AA'd can be assumed.</p>
	
	
	
