<br />
RytanEQ:<br />
Thank you for explaining the mana change was a blunder (as we had hoped it was).  Thank you also for eliminating the Daluda DoT and making it a heal.<br />
<br />
<b>Please upgrade Daluda's Mending</b> to 1800 hp healed (base).  In its current version, I do not feel it is enough.  In an environment where every mob mitigates slow, the current Daluda Mending spell is not powerful enough.  Though I understand your reasoning w/ the percentages per class, the GoD expansion w/ near 100% mitigation (of some kind) makes our 47% too weak.<br />
<br />
Thank you for listening,</p>
	
	
	
