</span></td>
	
	<td class="alt2" valign="top">
	
	<!-- message -->
	<p>Healing AAs and healing focii are two things that I worked on last in my recent AA and gear plan.  Mana pres and cold nuke focus is what I went for (max 1202 dmg for ~265mana is good, regardless of cast time).<br />
<br />
Just because you don't have the AAs doesn't mean you can't hang in Vxed/Tipt and beyond.  If you don't have the gear, though, you won't be able to.  You need lots of mana and lots of hitpoints.  That's not elitist, that's reality.  If you can't acquire the spell, then you don't need it. <br />
<br />
Again, that's not elitism, that's cold hard truth.</p>
	
	
	
